## 8. Challenges and Solutions

| Challenge | Root Cause | Solution | Learning |
|-----------|-----------|---------|---------|
| CSV column misalignment | Product names with commas, inferSchema=true | inferSchema=false + quote/escape options | Bronze should never interpret data — only ingest |
| fact_sales row count 23,487 | Duplicate product_id in dim_product causing fan-out | GROUP BY + MAX() on dim_product | Always test each join incrementally before committing |
| dim_location fan-out | Multiple postal codes per city | Remove postal_code, change grain to city+state | Dimension grain must match fact granularity |
| Role-playing date dimension | Two FKs to same dim table | Active + inactive relationship in Power BI, USERELATIONSHIP() in DAX | One dim table can serve multiple purposes |
| Silver type casting silent failures | Bad values cast to null without error | Null checks run after casting, not before | Cast first, check nulls second — casting creates nulls |

